y takes a photo prior to the Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.679873732230047e-24, \"text\": \"Stephen Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elena Rodriguez/Reuters  PARIS, France - Forget the medals.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top prize for many at the2024 Paris Olympicsis a shiny, heart-shaped Simone Biles pin.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, the most decorated gymnast in history, has arrived at the Games with a stash of gold-colored pin badges marked with her name to swap with fans and fellow competitors.\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People have been trading national team emblems and other souvenirs at Olympics events for years.\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But this time round, the enthusiastic involvement of the star US athlete, and a surprisingly long list of other top sporting names, has taken it all to a whole other level.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999051815058627, \"rank\": 9.274728118221367e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two-time NBA MVP Stephen Curry was spotted trading badges on the US team boat during theopening ceremonylast Friday, July 26.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 944, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"score\": 0.9240276609325847, \"rank\": 0.08221868487213069, \"text\": \"NBA MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\"}, {\"begin\": 952, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.679873732230047e-24, \"text\": \"Stephen Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\"}, {\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999051815058627, \"rank\": 9.274728118221367e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Curry has won virtually every trophy in professional basketball and his $55.8-million salary next season makes him the highest-paid player in the NBA.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1943365812226222e-12, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sente